#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:102
msgid ""
"How much of each place hierarchy is shown in chart arcs (full name, or only "
"the lowest 1–3 levels). Users toggle place visibility on/off in the chart "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Koliko svake hijerarhije mesta se prikazuje u lukovima grafikona (puni naziv "
"ili samo najnižih 1–3 nivoa). Korisnici uključuju ili isključuju prikaz "
"mesta u obrascu grafikona."

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml:59
msgid ""
"Images are only shown if the arc segment is wide enough. Images for "
"descendants are not yet available."
msgstr ""
"Slike se prikazuju samo ako je segment luka dovoljno širok. Slike za potomke "
"još uvek nisu dostupne."

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/page.phtml:41
msgid "Individual"
msgstr "Pojedinac"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/details.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Inserts the GEDCOM NICK value in quotes between the given names and the "
"surname (e.g. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Mirrors the legacy webtrees "
"behaviour for trees that store nicknames in the separate GEDCOM NICK field."
msgstr ""
"Umetne vrednost GEDCOM NICK u navodnicima između ličnih imena i prezimena "
"(npr. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Oponaša staro webtrees ponašanje za stabla "
"koja nadimke čuvaju u zasebnom polju GEDCOM NICK."

